author: Andres Salomon <dilinger@debian.org>
description: hardcode lld for clang-13

Upstream doesn't allow overridding the linker (other than toggling
lld vs gold). 


Index: chromium-103.0.5060.134/build/config/compiler/BUILD.gn
===================================================================
--- chromium-103.0.5060.134.orig/build/config/compiler/BUILD.gn
+++ chromium-103.0.5060.134/build/config/compiler/BUILD.gn
@@ -345,7 +345,7 @@ config("compiler") {
     }
 
     if (use_lld) {
-      ldflags += [ "-fuse-ld=lld" ]
+      ldflags += [ "-fuse-ld=lld-13" ]
       if (lld_path != "") {
         ldflags += [ "-B$lld_path" ]
       }
